snippet.title: Angler's Club: Ultimate Bass Fishing 3D - N3DS - Bubble Trailer
snippet.description:
Angler's Club: Ultimate Bass Fishing™ 3D captures the thrill of tournament style fishing by providing the most authentic and natural fishing experience on a handheld system in stunning 3D. Featuring over 40 championship tournaments, players can compete and win trophies using a variety of skills to become a world class fishing champion.

Angler's Club: Ultimate Bass Fishing 3D is scheduled for Summer 2011 on Nintendo 3DS.
